  <brief_title>A Prospective Clinical Study of a Cohort of Pathological or &quot;at Risk&quot; Gamblers Seeking Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Clinical Study of a Cohort of Pathological or &quot;at Risk&quot; Gamblers Seeking Treatment in the University Hospital of Nantes</official_title>
